            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Does a brand community need to be online?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Harley-Davidson's HOG chapters, CrossFit boxes, and local coffee-roaster meetups are offline communities. Most 2026 brand communities are hybrid — a digital hub with periodic in-person events.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">How is a brand community different from a Facebook page or an email list?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
